# Tailwind Integration (Frontend Local)

- Use `.postcssrc.json` as the PostCSS source of truth for this frontend project.
- Keep a single Tailwind entry import in `frontend/src/styles.css` using `@import 'tailwindcss';`.
- Do not add duplicate Tailwind imports in component styles or additional global files.
- Keep Tailwind setup in app-level styles/config; feature code should only use utility classes.
- If Tailwind stops working, first verify:
  - `.postcssrc.json` exists and has `@tailwindcss/postcss`
  - `frontend/src/styles.css` includes `@import 'tailwindcss';`
  - app build references `src/styles.css` in `angular.json`
